    <div class="clearfix" id="content">
     <div class="region region-content main clearfix">
      <div class="block block-system sixteen columns" id="block-system-main">
       <div class="block-content clearfix">
        <div about="/node/1" id="node-1" typeof="foaf:Document">
         <div class="node-content clearfix prose node-content clearfix prose">
          <div class="field field-name-body field-type-text-with-summary field-label-hidden prose">
           <div class="field-items">
            <div class="field-item even" property="content:encoded">
             <h2>
              Building Inclusion in the
              <br/>
              Sciences Through Research
             </h2>
             <p>
              Converge gathers, expands, disseminates and utilizes knowledge related to human resource development and human capital in the biomedical, behavioral science and high demand science, technology, engineering and mathematics (STEM) fields. Of particular interest are groups that are traditionally underrepresented in these fields.
             </p>
             <h3>
              Converge generates knowledge through:
             </h3>
             <ul>
              <li>
               Conducting rigorous, theory-based scientific
               <strong>
                research
               </strong>
              </li>
              <li>
               Linking
               <strong>
                policy and practice
               </strong>
               with scientific evidence
              </li>
              <li>
               <strong>
                Engaging
               </strong>
               multidisciplinary stakeholders
              </li>
             </ul>
             <p>
              Knowledge is created by Converge to advance social equity, inclusive excellence and economic competitiveness.
             </p>
             <p>
             </p>
            </div>
           </div>
          </div>
         </div>
         <div class="node-links clearfix">
         </div>
        </div>
       </div>
      </div>
      <div class="block block-block sixteen columns" id="block-block-17">
       <div class="block-content clearfix prose">
        <h3>
         “If we are to achieve a richer culture, rich in contrasting values, we must recognize the whole gamut of human potentialities, and so weave a less arbitrary social fabric, one in which
         <strong>
          each diverse human gift
         </strong>
         will find a fitting place.”
        </h3>
        <p>
         Margaret Mead
        </p>
       </div>
      </div>
     </div>
    </div>
   </div>
